     {"element":
      ["p",
       true,
       [],
       [{"text": "A very common pattern is "},
        {"element":
         ["code",
          true,
          [],
          [{"text": "field_simp;"}, {"text": " "}, {"text": "ring"}]]},
        {"text": " (clear denominators, then the resulting goal is"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text":
         "solvable by the axioms of a commutative ring). The finishing tactic "},
        {"element": ["code", true, [], [{"text": "field"}]]},
        {"text": " is a shorthand for this"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text": "pattern."}]]},
     {"element":
      ["p",
       true,
       [],
       [{"text":
         "Cancelling and combining denominators will generally require checking \"nonzeroness\"/\"positivity\""},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text": "side conditions. The "},
        {"element": ["code", true, [], [{"text": "field_simp"}]]},
        {"text":
         " tactic attempts to discharge these, and will omit such steps if it"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text":
         "cannot discharge the corresponding side conditions. The discharger will try, among other things,"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"element":
         ["code",
          true,
          [],
          [{"element":
            ["a",
             true,
             [["href", "./Mathlib/Tactic/Positivity/Core.html#positivity"]],
             [{"text": "positivity"}]]}]]},
        {"text": " and "},
        {"element":
         ["code",
          true,
          [],
          [{"element":
            ["a",
             true,
             [["href", "./Mathlib/Tactic/NormNum/Core.html#norm_num"]],
             [{"text": "norm_num"}]]}]]},
        {"text":
         ", and will also use any nonzeroness/positivity proofs included explicitly"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text": "(e.g. "},
        {"element":
         ["code",
          true,
          [],
          [{"text": "field_simp"}, {"text": " "}, {"text": "[hx]"}]]},
        {"text": "). If your expression is not completely reduced by "},
        {"element": ["code", true, [], [{"text": "field_simp"}]]},
        {"text": ", check the"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text":
         "denominators of the resulting expression and provide proofs that they are nonzero/positive to enable"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text": "further progress."}]]}]]},
